{"tid":406371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只有天真幼稚嘅人先信人人平等","createTime":"2017-09-19T14:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T16:37:11.000Z","uid":11779,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9eaf451cf4cee3963457fd9b79d41111d3d2044b","tid":406371,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T14:56:48.000Z","msg":"高官個仔先係人，人地個仔係數字<br />\n靚女港大生比樹壓死係新聞， I大豬扒比壓死係事故.<br />\n白人撞死黃種人係不幸，黃種人撞死白人係天理不容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明唔明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50b6863337e3c360713d3f00c6dcee446f086f2","tid":406371,"uid":38539,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"人終有一死，死神面前人人平等"},{"pid":"ef77366255c16dd1cd04ace4e6e9cfbc8786966d","tid":406371,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"平等係目標唔係現況"},{"pid":"0039700fbfe1c62a5dd5df1dfeae22bb874505e8","tid":406371,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:03:28.000Z","msg":"5毛又留低負皮"},{"pid":"8a65b5c5b9f114c31b4d5b55cad45c7c03f5dc63","tid":406371,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:06:15.000Z","msg":"唔係信唔信<br />\n而係你每一個行動結果 都只係想不平等<br />\n就連平等呢兩隻字<br />\n點去理解都係問題"},{"pid":"9797258fc3e7849a42a06a3db2736daa553548e3","tid":406371,"uid":53589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:23:53.000Z","msg":"相信人人平等同相信人人應該要平等係兩件事<br />\n你覺得平等呢個詞係點黎？ 就係因為人類社會出現種種不平等， 係資源， 經濟，政治上。 由以前奴隸，去到而家有錢人話事， 都係唔平等。但正因為咁平等自由係可貴， 我地要追求呢樣野，無論係合理既工作回報同社會資源分配，或者平等既政治參與權同反對在位者濫權，都係追求平等既行動"},{"pid":"915a409532dc1d741622518090db2ea8b223d958","tid":406371,"uid":99225,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T15:58:51.000Z","msg":"唔係信平等 現實係不平等<br />\n所以先追求平等"},{"pid":"c8a04024a605985c73d9aa401355e8f94620f59f","tid":406371,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高官個仔先係人，人地個仔係數字<br />\n靚女港大生比樹壓死係新聞， I大豬扒比壓死係事故.<br />\n白人撞死黃種人係不幸，黃種人撞死白人係天理不容<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明唔明？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黃你老母種人"},{"pid":"b67faf8eed69d20d0b809a0399de87c3edbc5d78","tid":406371,"uid":130118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"所有人平等<br />\n社會會缺少競爭動力，好難進步<br />\nMatrix都話一開始比人人開心，係唔work<br />\n有能者居之係社會運作基本<br />\n動物界都有食物鏈"},{"pid":"81246c9048c501f650e46ecd0c8ad2e8e88dc34e","tid":406371,"uid":49250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"現實面前 窮人含撚"},{"pid":"bb2d64923d06de40d4f4273ebad248ec02206c39","tid":406371,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:18:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平等係目標唔係現況</blockquote><br />\n由出世 小學考試温餐死就係為比隔離個個快半個馬位 製做對比其他人優勢既狀況 行為已經暴露晒目標 唔夠人鬥個陣就叫人平等<br />\n<br />\n目標 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所有人既人生目標就係比隔離個個高一等"},{"pid":"791f4a64758b95f7785644e49ec82a93996dc83b","tid":406371,"uid":27866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:22:33.000Z","msg":"係人都知啦 講經咩...."},{"pid":"ebf4602dfcd33da1ad35c7d5b1bf6821d440308d","tid":406371,"uid":683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平等係目標唔係現況</blockquote><br />\n由出世 小學考試温餐死就係為比隔離個個快半個馬位 製做對比其他人優勢既狀況 行為已經暴露晒目標 唔夠人鬥個陣就叫人平等<br />\n<br />\n目標 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所有人既人生目標就係比隔離個個高一等</blockquote><br />\n我溫書係想一百分炸，乜你小學就已經咁撚勾心鬥角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f192e92393a0ad67d43ab21056860af67e1f83","tid":406371,"u